<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08894</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT EXEMPTING PETROLEUM PRODUCTS FROM VALUE-ADDED TAX (VAT), AMENDING FOR THE PURPOSE SECTION 109 OF THE NATIONAL INTERNAL REVENUE CODE OF 1997, AS AMENDED</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Intends to alleviate the burden of fuel price hikes on the Filipino people thereby increasing the purchasing power of the public, especially those who belong to the lowest strata of our society.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>VARGAS, ALFRED D.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2019-01-29</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON WAYS AND MEANS ON 2019-02-04</td></tr></table>